title: Acker Bilk - Mellow Music
description:
After almost 6 Years of searching, mailing and God knows what. We finally found this album!
Mailing and writing Mr. Bilk and almost every related branch of his staff acquiring any info on how to obtain a copy of a master or a CD copy, We have taken it upon ourselves to give this out to all of you for free... (since the legitimate way didn't work...)
Seed everyone, maybe some brits learn humility of it...
